<p><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(240, 241, 255); font-size: 24px;">为激励经济管理学院学子关爱自我，关注身心健康，12月12日下午，经济管理学院组织班级在先锋小镇攀岩场开展大学生心理素质拓展活动。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 30.9999px; text-wrap: wrap; caret-color: rgb(255, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(240, 241, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240113/1705116528391057004.png" title="1705116528391057004.png" alt="61d81533b3c7162bd527f5d2c7e77ee4.png" width="955" height="341" style="width: 955px; height: 341px;"/></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(240, 241, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">看似不陡峭的岩壁，攀爬起来却没想象中容易，需要大家根据自身的观察，在不同高度和角度的岩壁上进行精准判断，向上攀登。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(240, 241, 255); text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">同学们在一次又一次的困难与挑战中不断突破自我，从最开始的胆怯、退缩、自我设限到勇敢的迈开步伐突破自我直至完成挑战，到回头一瞬间的满满成就感，收获的是满满的自信。</span></p>